results.deck: MumboJumbo is a casual game developer based out of Dallas, Texas.
results.description:
MumboJumbo has developed and published many adventure games, including the Midnight Mysteries series. They are also the creators of the Luxor puzzle game series.

In January 2007, MumboJumbo acquired Ritual Entertainment, developers of the SiN franchise.
